@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qyssbg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.50 / wp.abs((tmp + 0.72 * v2 + 0.92)))
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.abs(tmp + 0.66) - (tmp + 0.07 - v1 + 0.46)))
    v1 = 0.08
    data[tid] = v0
